OL,4,CHairdressers fear staff crisis after
OL,5,Capprentice shortage
OL,6, Hairdressers fear a future staffing
OL,7, crisis as the pandemic has caused the
OL,8, already decreasing number of
OL,9, apprentices to fall further.
OL,11,FThe number of people starting
OL,12,Fhairdressing apprenticeships in England
OL,13,Fhad halved between 2016 and 2020.
OL,15,FThe National Hair and Beauty Federation
OL,16,F(NHBF) expects another drop of 30 to
OL,17,F50% in the coming year.
OL,19,FThe skills minister said any employer
OL,20,Fwho took on a new apprentice before 30
OL,21,FSeptember 2021 would get #3,000.
